Package com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.lex.interactionkit.internal.audio

Class AudioStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.lex.interactionkit.internal.audio.AudioStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AudioSource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChunkedAudioStream
    public class AudioStream
extends java.lang.Object
implements AudioSource
    An AudioSource that writes a stream of audio to the network connection. Currently only audio/x-l16, audio/x-l16preamble, and audio/x-cbr-opus-preamble are supported.
